643
00:33:30,550 --> 00:33:32,510
I didn’t mean to kill her.

644
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:35,000
It was a mistake.

645
00:33:35,750 --> 00:33:37,960
I was protecting state property.

646
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,110
I didn’t mean to kill.

