720
00:38:57,230 --> 00:39:00,280
Ding Baoyuan wouldn’t kill Cheng Chun

721
00:39:00,630 --> 00:39:01,920
over blackmail.

722
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:05,590
So according to you,

723
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:07,000
Ding Baoyuan had no motive to kill,

724
00:39:07,710 --> 00:39:09,150
